; Regression test for bug #2355: balance assertions should preserve lot
; annotations.  When transferring between brokerage accounts using a
; balance assignment, the cost basis and lot date must be preserved.

2024/01/01 * Old Broker
    Assets:Brokerage:Old       100 FOO @ $123
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/02 * New Broker
    Assets:Brokerage:Old               =0
    Assets:Brokerage:New

test bal --lots --flat '^Assets:Brokerage:New'
100 FOO {$123} [2024/01/01]  Assets:Brokerage:New
end test
